txt.en: Unudhu was second in command at the Library, but his hopes of promotion were cut short.
Piztor schemed to replace Unudhu as Gûrsh's second, only to be thwarted by you.
Defeat the leaders of the invasion of the Library at Tham Mírdain.
Chieftain Gûrsh once led the forces of the White Hand ransacking Tham Mírdain, but no more, thanks to you.
